---
title: Cheesy Chicken Enchiladas with guacamole and tomato salsa
description: Enchiladas are a traditional Mexican dish, usually oven baked, which feature tortillas filled with all sorts of delicious fillings. This dish is cheesy, filled with chicken and topped with freshly mixed guacamole.
